bib:Article.dcterms:abstract:
Chapter of the Cathedral of Siguenze 150, one plate of which precedes the article;
ms dated to around 900 CE on the basis especially of the Latin script. No Arabic text, but a literal
French translation of Gal. 1:1-15 with commentary.
